{
  "stem": "9601.7",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And one day he was telling about this problem in this story.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He kept using the word troublous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And over, troublous here, troublous there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "All kinds of little incidents with the word troublous.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "No one could figure out what is troublous.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he went up to the blackboard and he wrote it out, troubles, T-R-O-U-B-L-E-S.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That's-- you pronounce it, you know, the way it's written, by sound, but not the English way, troubles.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It's troublous.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "That was very, very cute.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We had such a terrific laugh.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "That's what his nickname became, Troublous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was the first summer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I was sent to high school, so I continued going to Northern High School, which was, I didn't know how about it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was out of my district.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, naturally, I had a very difficult time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was mixed already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Didn't make any difference.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A student is a student.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But let me tell you that I did not-- I looked at myself now-- that I did not react-- I'm not sure how to say-- I had no big reaction because I was in a school with blacks and whites, or Afro Americans.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we were in Germany, when we crossed the border, we were there for a week in a camp called Hof.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was at the Czech-German border and there was a big United States Army camp, installation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I used to see these soldiers walking back and forth all over by the gates.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Must have been a black division, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know, an American blacks division.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was the first time in my life that I saw an Afro American.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It's fascinating.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, they said black people, but how can you imagine what they look like?",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
